casebody.data:
Fourth Department,

December, 1958

(December 17, 1958) Carol Brown, Appellant, v. State of New York, Respondent. (Claim No. 32608.)

Judgment affirmed, without costs of this appeal to either party. All concur, Kimball, J., not participating. (Appeal from a judgment of the Court of Claims for claimant on a claim for personal injuries alleged to have been sustained by reason of negligent condition of State highway.) Present — MeCum, P. J., Kimball, Bastow, Goldman and Halpern, JJ.
